\n            </div>\n            <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white font-heading mb-4\" data-kid=\"170\">AI Processing</h3>\n            <p class=\"text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"171\">Our neural networks analyze your data against 10M+ local transactions and current market trends instantly.</p>\n          </div>\n\n          \n          <div class=\"group relative p-8 bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800/80 rounded-[2rem] hover:border-yellow-400/30 transition-all duration-300 shadow-xl\" data-kid=\"172\">\n             <div class=\"absolute -top-4 left-8 w-10 h-10 bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 text-yellow-400 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center font-black text-lg\" data-kid=\"173\">3</div>\n            <div class=\"mb-8 pt-4\" data-kid=\"174\">\n              <div class=\"w-14 h-14 bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center border border-slate-800 group-hover:bg-slate-800 transition-colors\" data-kid=\"175\">\n                 <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#facc15\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" data-kid=\"176\"><path d=\"M14.5 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7.5L14.5 2z\" data-kid=\"177\"></path><polyline points=\"14 2 14 8 20 8\" data-kid=\"178\"></polyline><path d=\"m9 15 2 2 4-4\" data-kid=\"179\"></path></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white font-heading mb-4\" data-kid=\"180\">Get Appraisal</h3>\n            <p class=\"text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"181\">Download a comprehensive PDF report with valuation ranges, confidence scores, and local market intelligence.</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    \n    <section class=\"py-32 px-6\" data-kid=\"182\">\n      <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto\" data-kid=\"183\">\n        <div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-2